data.title: Nationals Invitational 2013
data.meta_description: Results, race videos and interviews from the 2013 Brooks Pre-National Invitational hosted by the Indiana State University in Terre Haute on Saturday, October 19, 2013. Flotrack will be on hand to cover the invitational for the seventh consecutive year!
